{"tid":384320,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得其實火影入面努力先係最強","createTime":"2017-09-02T08:07:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T22:45:36.000Z","uid":82889,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"60e1989d9e31b3c1aea47b70992d12df6511f9bc","tid":384320,"uid":82889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:07:14.000Z","msg":"本身去到夜凱之前都仲係血統&gt;努力<br />\n但去到夜凱打爆斑呢個有血統+後天拎柱間細胞+殺細佬+吸尾獸<br />\n留意番斑係呢個時候已經係神既lv,就連鳴人佐助合力都只係同佢打和<br />\n去到故事最尾,鳴人同佐助都已經冇左陽之力同陰之力,即係連斑一半都冇<br />\n換言之如果係疾風傳後小李出到夜凱既話,根本完全係可以一擊就收哂佢兩個皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n理論上如果小李有凱咁勁,咁佢開八門就一定勁過博人傳既鳴佐,最多係唔夠拎哂九隻尾獸同陰陽力既斑打,不過前題係佢要犧牲條命<br />\n<br />\n一個普通人靠努力可以去到只次於神一級,咁其實火影都冇大家講到咁血統論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad9c33c7fad5399bffcfdffc64b62e13e714df4e","tid":384320,"uid":63670,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:12:35.000Z","msg":"人地有血統，輕輕鬆鬆就成神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你努力，仲要用命換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要係半神<br />\n<br />\n努力最強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"8b03552353ca36eb0ca4ed7e161c679b2189989c","tid":384320,"uid":138752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:16:24.000Z","msg":"小李連七門都開唔到喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eeb53378af558ef9a7e670d22b2efe8f6e54429","tid":384320,"uid":132605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:17:38.000Z","msg":"其實只係龜兔賽跑 班係有先天優勢<br />\n但班唔努力只想走捷徑 咩都唔做拎晒尾獸力量 然後變成六道狀態"},{"pid":"0447975357f16b392b65a2b2287bb58507838625","tid":384320,"uid":3179,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:17:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地有血統，輕輕鬆鬆就成神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你努力，仲要用命換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要係半神<br />\n<br />\n努力最強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n斑個計劃 用盡左佢一身既心血<br />\n輕輕鬆鬆？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8c73a511ea92cc2fb18c26f4459e996936a9255","tid":384320,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:19:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ca984cb0f32fdd329b66561602e2066136ad1ea","tid":384320,"uid":72608,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:23:32.000Z","msg":"點努力都好,千鳥都係勁唔過雷切"},{"pid":"1163b27263a1ed9f71b5209b9c45e6d9ec47bc8e","tid":384320,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:25:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對阿李出招幻術由佢打空氣打到斷腳都傷唔到人半條毛啦</blockquote><br />\n班既幻術好廢"},{"pid":"b97b804faeaa5731a3741bb38dc8c52d93639775","tid":384320,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:25:56.000Z","msg":"有名你叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 血統忍者喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170af27d836f67c64f8c406ab1a9013920978e52","tid":384320,"uid":82889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:30:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小李連七門都開唔到喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n博人傳任佢吹啦"},{"pid":"dae89607a5cb22fd295e6e28a549e2853279609f","tid":384320,"uid":82889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:32:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人地有血統，輕輕鬆鬆就成神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你努力，仲要用命換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要係半神<br />\n<br />\n努力最強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n斑個計劃 用盡左佢一身既心血<br />\n輕輕鬆鬆？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對連登仔黎講天才既付出唔係付出黎,因為所有野都係輕輕鬆鬆就做到,點叫付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35d1cdf699fbb06ea3ba20fbbcee2f5d05d6aa2","tid":384320,"uid":82889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:32:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對阿李出招幻術由佢打空氣打到斷腳都傷唔到人半條毛啦</blockquote><br />\n咁你講撚哂啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n任何勁招都係廢招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e04a2bf3152081e05c2b910991388e255012bb","tid":384320,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:34:14.000Z","msg":"佐助既萬花筒，永恆萬花筒同輪迴眼都係尼桑同六道送比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aadf9f6e107dbe5c333776939dc4cb1837b9d4b3","tid":384320,"uid":82889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:35:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佐助既萬花筒，永恆萬花筒同輪迴眼都係尼桑同六道送比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇意思,送哂比佢都係唔夠八門勁"},{"pid":"c607768fe845bdffac5978093f88de9f22e8ced1","tid":384320,"uid":82889,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:39:03.000Z","msg":"呢到好多野都係到講變強既過程<br />\n我係直接比較緊結果,因為唔駛睇冇血統用努力既過程一定係辛苦百倍千倍<br />\n但出黎既結果係就算鳴人有九尾有仙人都會比八門夜凱一擊KO<br />\n所以小李係THE LAST培訓左班八門小隊出黎係正路既<br />\n犧牲其中一個就可以擋到一次世界末日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e6eea0725f2196b8bd50b835ac6d9daf655503","tid":384320,"uid":82889,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:44:42.000Z","msg":"預左會多負皮,不過都改變唔到八門夜凱勁過哂咩鳴佐九尾仙人輪迴眼須佐既事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"077580cfd31304579068625b5d1a5e4cc3adba23","tid":384320,"uid":109557,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:55:20.000Z","msg":"夜凱幾勁都唔會打得贏多重影手裏劍"},{"pid":"e8335ddcc2b20d9c0d39b3703af0e75c5c902ba1","tid":384320,"uid":135336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T09:32:37.000Z","msg":"我記得前面有提過小李都係武術天才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打加拿嗰陣年紀小小就已經開到第五門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反而成日贏凱神啲挑戰嘅精英忍者卡卡西都只能夠開到3門<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d56cd1038850f943bf9c2bca894f52f542281e","tid":384320,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T09:47:32.000Z","msg":"(最強)"},{"pid":"1f9c836f736ad864d934e9f63a7b208a114789b3","tid":384320,"uid":27541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T10:47:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我記得前面有提過小李都係武術天才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打加拿嗰陣年紀小小就已經開到第五門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反而成日贏凱神啲挑戰嘅精英忍者卡卡西都只能夠開到3門<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n前面有講過小李既體術一開頭好廢<br />\n係死操爛操先開到5門"},{"pid":"d70a001bb65630df161bf0831279e4a46fc0e052","tid":384320,"uid":82404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T10:56:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我記得前面有提過小李都係武術天才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打加拿嗰陣年紀小小就已經開到第五門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反而成日贏凱神啲挑戰嘅精英忍者卡卡西都只能夠開到3門<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n前面有講過小李既體術一開頭好廢<br />\n係死操爛操先開到5門</blockquote><br />\n但呢個年紀就算係死操爛操都唔會開到五門<br />\n所以卡卡西先話佢係體術既天才"},{"pid":"840daea0298eb96452a92cde9d237fa72e58e09d","tid":384320,"uid":1993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T10:58:05.000Z","msg":"努力的天才"},{"pid":"1a9914f3dcff76f4e12ee82538b770ba1a8